HEADWORD: Undergrow
<hw>Un`der*grow"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To grow to an
inferior, or less than the usual, size or height.</def>
<rj><au>Wyclif.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

